Scilab-based scientific computing resource
Climate modeling and simulation tools
Data analysis and visualization
space.math
Mathematical models for space and climate interactions
Atmospheric and orbital calculations
Space-based climate observation algorithms
universe code data
Comprehensive data processing code
Universal data format handlers
Integration tools for multiple data sources
README.md
Repository documentation
