DATA SOURCES AND FORMATS
Supported Climate Data Sources
Global Climate Datasets:
CRU TS (Climatic Research Unit Time-Series): 1901-2022
ERA5 Reanalysis: 1940-2023
MERRA-2: 1980-present
UDEL (University of Delaware): 1900-2017
GPCC (Global Precipitation Climatology Centre)
WorldClim high-resolution climate data
Variable Types:
Temperature (mean, maximum, minimum)
Precipitation (rain, snow, total)
Wind speed and direction
Humidity and evapotranspiration
Cloud cover
Sea level pressure
Solar radiation
Spatial Resolutions:
0.25° × 0.25° (approximately 28 km)
0.5° × 0.5° (approximately 56 km)
Country and sub-national administrative levels
Custom regional grids
Temporal Resolutions:
Daily
Monthly
Seasonal
Annual
Multi-decadal
